{"tid":533772,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(食評) AV女星: Donald Trump的床上功夫差勁","createTime":"2018-01-19T06:53:28.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-20T02:46:33.000Z","uid":134071,"like":30,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":50,"replies":[{"pid":"cbe8d136d50debf020222fd0e6104a9e464448f6","tid":533772,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-19T06:53:28.000Z","msg":"AV女星Stormy Daniels以前曾指自己係2006年同特朗普扑過野, 而且性能力差勁.  《華爾街日報》指特朗普後來給予Stormy Daniels十三萬美金作為封口費.  <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.newsweek.com/donald-trump-bad-bed-porn-star-stormy-daniels-claimed-they-had-affair-nearly-783332\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.newsweek.com%2Fdonald-trump-bad-bed-porn-star-stormy-daniels-claimed-they-had-affair-nearly-783332&d=Q26sThRywBPecVqUHaKi6E%2FDJpISyAq9ELy6OyFxwDc%3D&h=a129936b\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.newsweek.com/donald-trump-bad-bed-porn-star-stormy-daniels-claimed-they-had-affair-nearly-783332</a><br />\n<br />\nDONALD TRUMP IS BAD IN BED, PORN STAR STORMY DANIELS CLAIMS, BUT THEY HAD AN AFFAIR FOR 'NEARLY A YEAR' ANYWAY: REPORT<br />\nBY TUFAYEL AHMED ON 1/17/18 AT 5:39 AM<br />\n<br />\nUpdated | The plot thickens in the curious case of President Donald Trump and his alleged dalliance with porn star Stormy Daniels.<br />\n<br />\nTrump&rsquo;s personal lawyer Michael Cohen denied Friday that Trump had a sexual encounter with the adult film star, after a Wall Street Journal report claimed the president arranged a $130,000 payout to Daniels to keep quiet about it. The Journal also said it received a two-paragraph statement attributed to Daniels, but sent to the paper by Cohen, which denied a sexual affair with Trump and said reports of &ldquo;hush money&rdquo; were &ldquo;completely false.&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\nOn Tuesday, Slate Editor-in-Chief Jacob Weisberg published a piece appearing to support the Journal settlement claims.<br />\n..........<br />\nDaniels reportedly told Weisberg that Trump was bad in bed, though in not so many words. &ldquo;She intimated that her view of his sexual skill was at odds with the remark attributed to Marla Maples,&rdquo; he wrote, linking to a Reddit post featuring an old New York Post cover touting Trump&rsquo;s ex-wife apparently saying: &ldquo;Best sex I&rsquo;ve ever had.&rdquo;"},{"pid":"8fabe5a643e690b844d04fb84041478190746f5f","tid":533772,"uid":134071,"like":38,"dislike":2,"score":36,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-19T06:54:17.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20180119/1281512/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20180119%2F1281512%2F&d=Q26sThRywBPecVqUHaKi6E%2FDJpISyAq9ELy6OyFxwDc%3D&h=7347dfc0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20180119%2F1281512%2F&h=69ecc390\" target=\"_blank\">http://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20180119/1281512/</a><br />\n<br />\n「暴風丹妮爾斯」在專訪中表示，當年川普盛讚自己的美貌與智慧，可與他女兒伊凡卡(Ivanka Trump)媲美，二人是在瑪蓮妮雅(Melania Trump)替他產下幼子拜倫(Barron Trump)後不久、2006年七月在內華達州一場高爾夫球比賽中相遇，很快就打得火熱，「不管你是不是他的粉絲，你得承認，他實在很迷人」。<strong>川普曾多次和她在大飯店「開房間」，川普每次都「無套，且只有單一體位」，「就像一般人在他那個年紀能做的一樣」，「一點也不瘋狂」。</strong>"},{"pid":"a8c4c7f734031f49284ff06442e3c9a14cff239f","tid":533772,"uid":154111,"like":208,"dislike":1,"score":207,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-19T06:55:48.000Z","msg":"06年個陣佢都60歲啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c08d29efc975bfb441ed8f6c904b06aa4ec8e78","tid":533772,"uid":5077,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-19T07:01:53.000Z","msg":"米九二，係幾吸引嘅"},{"pid":"75c6b10de1cbcf2bdd6aea5e025914072ce32092","tid":533772,"uid":57705,"like":134,"dislike":1,"score":133,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-19T07:03:32.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"413af26534150d003acfd8a0087fcff7029c582b","tid":533772,"uid":4285,"like":50,"di